Citation.sTitle: Isothermal vapor liquid equilibria for different binary mixtures involved in the alcoholic distillation
Citation.sAbstract: Isothermal vapor liquid equilibrium (VLE) data for five binary systems ethyl acetate + 3-methyl-1-butanol, ethanol + 3-methyl-1-butanol, ethyl acetate + 2-methyl-1-butanol, ethanol + 2-methyl-1-butanol, ethyl acetate + 2-methyl-1-propanol, involved in the alcoholic distillation have been determined experimentally by headspace gas chromatography. The composition in the liquid phase was corrected with the help of an iterative method by means of a GE model. However, due to the large density difference between the liquid and the vapor, the correction of the liquid phase composition is nearly negligible.
